  "label": "Cinderwake Cable Locker",
  "description": "A compact storage room set off the Cinderwake Cableway, enclosed by soot-dark plating and rib-braced bulkheads tarred along their rivet lines against ash intrusion. Racks of coiled line, spare turnbuckles, and bundled mast stays are lashed to iron stanchions with webbing straps, leaving a narrow aisle down the center. The deck bears grit-scour and shallow drainage channels, while tether rings are sunk into the plating to restrain cargo under electrostatic gale-roll. Lantern light filters through a shuttered glass cowl, reducing the room to hard-edged slits of illumination and deep, enduring shadow.",
